    "Metadata": {
        "Title": "From the Clubbers With Love",
        "Description": "Good evening 47,\r\rthe secret organisation SPECTACLE (Strategic Phantom Espionage and Covert Tactical Assault Command League Echelon) has hired a cluster of assassins to eliminate you after you took out their wooden handed operative Professor Yes. \r\rWe don&apos;t have much intel, they work under the names Donald Grant, Rosa Klebb and Krilencu. They will be undercover at the night club and surely use different names.\r\rFind them and take them out, before they get to you.\r\rI will leave you to prepare.\r\rThis contract was created by a member of the HITMAN community known as lostinweb83.",
